comment.author: 41490240@N06
comment._content: All the airial photos and most of those of the Mullahs Fort at Taleh must have been taken between 30 Dec 1919 and March 1920. The aircraft are DH9's of Z Force Commanded by Group Capt Gordon RAF. The aircraft were landed fromHMS Ark Royal and flown to El Dur Elan by 19 Feb 1920 and then commenced operations.
